&lt;p&gt;This post contains some research notes so don’t expect great quality, this is just to document how I go around devising a solution so you don’t assume me as some systems programming wizard.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I will merge my notes from earlier in first note and will add dates to later notes.&lt;/p&gt;
